WEBVTT

00:02:59.437 --> 00:03:02.322
He snips it, throws the tip
over his shoulder,

00:03:02.346 --> 00:03:04.662
and then grabs the scrotum
and pushes it upward,

00:03:04.686 --> 00:03:08.585
and then his head dips down,
obscuring my view.

00:03:08.609 --> 00:03:10.816
But what I hear is a slurping sound,

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:14.753
and a noise that sounds like Velcro
being yanked off a sticky wall,

00:03:14.777 --> 00:03:16.180
and I am not even kidding.

00:03:17.724 --> 00:03:18.877
Can we roll the video?

00:03:18.901 --> 00:03:20.243
No, I'm kidding, we don't --

00:03:20.267 --> 00:03:22.263
(Laughter)

00:03:22.287 --> 00:03:24.527
I thought it best to talk in pictures.

00:03:25.266 --> 00:03:29.271
I do something now I've never, ever done
on a "Dirty Jobs" shoot, ever.

00:03:29.295 --> 00:03:30.976
I say, "Time out. Stop."